The Bank of China will become acard-issuing member of &lt;Visa International> this year, Visa'schief general manager for Asia, Carl Pascarella, said in astatement.    Visa is designing a card for China, where internationalcredit cards are accepted but not yet issued.    He said Visa was developing training programs for the bankon card issuance and processing procedures. A Chinese groupwill visit Visa's San Francisco headquarters next month todiscuss future cooperation, he said. REUTER&#3;